Read dummy Phecode Map 1.2 with ICD-10 codes (beta) file into R

Source: R/dummy.R
read_icd10_phecode_map_dummy.Rd

Reads a dummy Phecode Map 1.2 with ICD-10 codes (beta) file into R (full version may be downloaded from phewascatalog.org)

Usage

read_icd10_phecode_map_dummy()

Value

A data frame.

See also

Other Dummy data: build_all_lkps_maps_dummy(), dummy_all_lkps_maps_path(), dummy_caliber_dir_path(), dummy_clinical_events_tidy(), dummy_icd10_phecode_map_path(), dummy_phecode_lkp_path(), dummy_ukb_codings_path(), read_all_lkps_maps_dummy(), read_phecode_lkp_dummy(), read_ukb_codings_dummy()
